  "id": "RAW_68b0cf06",
  "title": "CES 大腕儿最多的场子，诞生了第一个「AI 产业链」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&mid=2653096873&idx=1&sn=88e38962b4c2fb89420de761aca670c2",
  "date": "2026-01-09 08:29:00",
  "author": "极客公园",
  "siteName": "极客公园",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:0em;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;vertical-align:bottom;width:100%;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVd3yIwYCaJKyibia8G5B2NiacWicrMsfXPEt4beSBGL9ZHLpUG4gY2oPticgg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"341\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505613215\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=940480f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVd3yIwYCaJKyibia8G5B2NiacWicrMsfXPEt4beSBGL9ZHLpUG4gY2oPticgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:25px 18px 18px;margin:-0.6em 8px 2em;background-size:100%;letter-spacing:0.3px;clear:both;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8em;background-position:100% 100%;background-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr816\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">从「硬件巨头」到「AI 全栈方案提供商」。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:25px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrs0c\"><span leaf=\"\">作者｜</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">张勇毅&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrrzh\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑｜</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">靖宇</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:48px 8px 25px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrszg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在金庸的《倚天屠龙记》里，张无忌在昆仑山谷中苦练九阳神功，出谷时虽衣衫褴褛，却已是内力震世，举手投造间尽显宗师气象。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1lfr\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">2026 年 1 月的拉斯维加斯，全球目光聚焦在那个如科幻电影般巨大的 Sphere 建筑上。当联想集团董事长兼 CEO 杨元庆站在这个全场满座、一票难求的「科技神庙」中央时，这种「厚积薄发、一剑封喉」的既视感达到了顶峰。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrtrz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果说 2025 年全年，联想展现的都是初露锋芒的内力，那么在 CES 2026 上，联想展示的则是这股内力在打通了「任督二脉」后的一次全面爆发。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1m2p\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">从能随手卷曲、自由定义尺寸的卷轴屏 PC，到承载着全球 60 亿人期待的 2026 世界杯 AI 行动纲领，再到重定义人机交互入口的个人超级智能体 Lenovo Qira，联想正在完成从「硬件巨头」到「AI 全栈方案提供商」的终极跨越。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk6l8c5ipn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mroqr\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr237p\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">拒绝赢者通吃</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1b2w\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在武学中，内功的深浅决定了招式的上限，联想在 AI 时代的「内功心法」，被杨元庆总结为「混合式人工智能」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr15ds\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">杨元庆在演讲中也剖析了这一概念：他认为 AI 不仅仅是能写代码、画图的公有大模型，更是与个人数据深度融合的个人 AI，以及赋能企业价值链各个环节的企业 AI。这种个人智能、企业智能与公共智能的结合，构成了联想这次展示的核心主题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"770\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a52eac5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVdHt7fcNnp2zbPEvW6Kbj9yWmwAWk3pkwYBU2WibpRvw4CbAzV8Ez6zdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrl0e\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">杨元庆在接受媒体采访 ｜ 图片来源：联想</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr2171\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">但说到底，现在的 AI 发展已经进入了「下半场」，如何让技术落到实处、普及到每个角落才是关键。杨元庆认为，虽然公共智能很有用，能回答问题或产生视频，但它无法利用那些需要隐私保护的个人或企业数据。真正有意义的 AI，应该像九阳神功一样，能够赋能于人，让人的记忆力、创造力变得更强，让企业的工作效率更高，而不是追求一个在所有领域都比人强的虚无缥缈的 AGI。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr10mu\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">有趣的是，这种赋能逻辑也体现在联想对生态合作的态度上。在 Tech World 现场，英伟达、英特尔、AMD、高通这芯片界的「四大天王」悉数到场，这种排场在海外科技界确实罕见。杨元庆坦言，联想有着清晰的战略和扎实的创新成果，这些合作伙伴非常愿意来「捧场」，因为大家是互补的关系，而不是谁取代谁。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66675\" data-w=\"4000\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c09f9247&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVd4Xl5I7otjjickcg1KcQiaibibpLE8kGpHicLNWdpX8XrlB9NnFqqGvUR0lA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrbq8\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">Tech World 成为本次 CES 阵容最耀眼的会场｜ 图片来源：联想</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr10qc\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个时代，没有一家厂商能赢者通吃，硬件依然是用户进入 AI 的入口，但联想会选择在 AI 云、终端 PC 或小型穿戴设备上，分别与最顶尖的芯片商协作，共同把蛋糕做大。</span></strong></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk6la5aszou\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr8l3\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr149e\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">超级智能体：</span></span></strong></p>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr156u\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">那个越用越懂你的「大脑」</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrupw\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果说混合式 AI 是心法，那么联想这次发布的个人超级智能体 Lenovo Qira 就是这套武功的「大脑」。联想集团高级副总裁兼 CTO Tolga Kurtoglu 解释说，Qira 标志着 AI 从「应用级」向「系统级」的跨越。它不再只是一个简单的语音助手，而是一个打通了联想 PC、平板及摩托罗拉手机生态壁垒的超级入口。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-w=\"1200\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=14313916&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVd2K7KuczxfGJtx82LuUHWm8CMINlQ9bDtNhk8kHCibDTTgrO3baenUlA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr4zm\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">Tech World 主会场展示的 Qira 概念｜ 图片来源：联想</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr17uq\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">Qira 的底层有三大核心技术支撑：模型编排、智能体核心引擎以及多智能体协作。首先，模型编排技术能像指挥家一样，根据用户的特定任务，挑选出最合适的单一模型或组合模型矩阵。其次，智能体核心引擎则赋予了 Qira「认知能力」，让它能理解用户的上下文语境和真实意图，拥有长期和短期的记忆，甚至能把复杂的任务拆解成简单的步骤去执行。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr3kt\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">体现在实际使用上，就是 Qira 几乎能预判你的需求，代表你执行任务。它深度集成在系统层，可以通过「Hey, Qira」语音唤醒，也可以静默在后台待命，甚至在离线状态下跨应用、跨设备执行操作，大幅减少了在不同 App 之间切换的繁琐。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk6laxgg1myn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrlvt\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrf6w\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">卷轴屏与不被尺寸定义的未来</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrt0m\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">作为联想的传统长板，在硬件形态的探索上，联想展示了一系列突破想象力的「奇门兵刃」。硬件不再是体验的起点，而是承载 AI 智能体验的载体，这种「软件驱动硬件」的逻辑在卷轴屏概念机上体现得淋漓尽致。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mri6r\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">最具视觉冲击力的是拯救者 Pro Rollable 概念机。这台 16 寸的游戏本内部安装了一块可卷曲的 PureSight OLED 屏幕，通过双电机驱动，支持在 16 寸、21.5 寸和 24 寸三种形态间热切换。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-w=\"3000\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=06fe601a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVdia0zJTbm4wx5q7sNXFPe2YyRTf2ibmibTxQD01J722uXVcfPWQoSQbQjg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr6zb\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">拯救者 Pro Rollable 概念机｜ 图片来源：联想</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1gd9\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">而 ThinkPad 家族的 Rollable XD 概念机则展示了另一种可能。这款机器采用了全球首批外折结构设计，屏幕可以从 13.3 寸向上延展到近 16 寸，多出来的屏幕面积超过了 50%，却不需要用户携带笨重的 16 寸本子。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-w=\"1536\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4dd7f2fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVdia7Xoyt4s4icXsRp1ia8HC0ZdW9JGpsZSiauicPjIIYQtLyDiarHCwBdOeXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrw33\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">Rollable XD 概念机｜ 图片来源：联想</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrlzk\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">有趣的是，多余的屏幕并不是收纳进机身，而是绕到了 A 面，并且覆盖了 180 度的康宁大猩猩玻璃保护，即便在闭合状态下也能进行交互。对于那些需要在便携机身里实现大屏办公的专业人士来说，这台保留了小红点的机器确实诱惑力十足。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr146y\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">此外，联想还展示了自动旋转转轴的 ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist，它能通过 AI 视觉追踪用户位置自动调整屏幕角度。甚至还有只有 45 克重的 Lenovo AI Glasses Concept，配合 Qira 可以实现实时翻译、图像识别和 OCR 提取，续航长达 8 小时。这些设备都证明了一点：联想正在把未来的可能性提前摆上我们的桌面。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mre16\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在移动端，摩托罗拉作为联想的先锋，也在这次 CES 上打出了一套漂亮的连招。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrfeh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">首先是众望所归的 Razr Fold 大折叠屏手机，这不仅是对「希望 moto 出一台平价大折叠」呼声的回应，更是摩托罗拉在折叠屏领域积累五年后的亮剑。这款机器拥有 8 寸的 2K 内屏，维持了 razr 系列一贯良好的折痕控制，并支持新款手写笔 Moto Pen Ultra。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.70703125\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"409\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c6df524&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVdxQNW1Scgw6ftcTPnE8ib8Ziapic69EFzuUmcvFra0wBvTibOsR7WmBicAaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1cs1\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">Razr Fold 大折叠屏手机｜ 图片来源：联想</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1ikw\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">除了折叠屏，摩托罗拉还重启了直板旗舰线，推出了瞄准 7000 元以上市场的 moto Signature。这款机器延续了 edge 系列的沉稳格调，采用骁龙 8 Gen 5 处理器，并提供夸张的 7 次 Android 版本升级和 7 年安全更新。它配备了 6.8 寸 165Hz 的直屏，峰值亮度达到 6200 尼特，甚至还通过了军规认证。这种在系统干净度、硬件耐用性和长期维护上的投入，显示了联想重塑摩托罗拉高端形象的决心。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk6lchy27x4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1uf7\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">04</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr6u2\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">下「笨功夫」的执着</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1x5n\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果说 AI 创新和酷炫的卷轴屏是联想的「面子」，那么在隐私安全、全球化交付这些用户平时不太注意的「里子」上，联想则展现出一种大厂特有的、下「笨功夫」的执着。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1kgx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">杨元庆在访谈中还提到，联想落实全球化结合本地化策略已久，形成了「全球资源、本地交付」的完善体系。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1okl\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这种底气让他们在赞助 F1 和世界杯时游刃有余。例如在 F1 赛事中，联想不仅提供 PC 和服务器，还部署了海神液冷技术，在提升计算性能的同时提高了 40% 的能效。这种针对不同赛事苛刻需求的定制化能力，正是联想内功深厚的体现。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr185\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在隐私保护上，联想坚持「人本智能」的科技价值观。而在 AI 时代，联想通过混合式架构平衡了云端功能与本地隐私，让用户始终拥有知情权和选择权。这种克制与严谨，决定了联想神功大成时内力的精纯。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-w=\"2048\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8cd73456&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5ZsQKqAMJzVyNSicjg0vykVdzzynXib7xsLIeyEiaAnp03dahfBZ2hRtZL5wGNyUWEhBwn6lwicb1XnpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1nii\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：联想</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mr1gsc\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">联想在 2026 年 CES 上展示的一切，本质上都是研发领域多年持续投入所带来的「质变」。从卷轴屏的形态创新到 Qira 的智能协同，从 F1 的液冷技术到世界杯的 AI 行动纲领，一个更加立体、更具创新活力的联想已经破谷而出。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk6le7mrrz8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">江湖的新秩序正在被打破，而联想在这个新江湖里的故事，才刚刚翻开最精彩的一页。在这个以用户为中心、建立在信任基础上的 AI 新时代，联想已经准备好带领我们走进那个更智能、更公平的未来。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "聚焦 CES 2026，联想展示了从“硬件巨头”向“AI 全栈方案提供商”的转型，发布了“混合式人工智能”战略、个人超级智能体 Qira 和一系列创新 AI 硬件。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "聚焦 CES 2026，联想展示了从“硬件巨头”向“AI 全栈方案提供商”的转型，发布了“混合式人工智能”战略、个人超级智能体 Qira 和一系列创新 AI 硬件。",
  "summary": "文章报道了联想在 2026 年 CES 展会上展现的最新成果和战略转型。联想不再仅是硬件巨头，正向“AI 全栈方案提供商”迈进。核心观点是联想提出的“混合式人工智能”，即结合个人 AI、企业 AI 和公共智能，旨在赋能个体和企业，而非追求通用人工智能。文章详细介绍了联想发布的个人超级智能体 Lenovo Qira，该智能体通过模型编排、智能体核心引擎及多智能体协作，跨设备、跨应用地理解用户意图并执行任务。此外，联想还展示了多款创新硬件产品，如可自由定义尺寸的卷轴屏 PC、外折叠屏幕笔记本、AI 眼镜以及新款摩托罗拉折叠屏手机和旗舰直板机，强调硬件是承载 AI 体验的载体。文章最后指出联想在隐私安全和全球化交付等“里子”工程上的“笨功夫”投入，体现了其在研发上的长期积累和对“人本智能”价值观的坚持。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "联想正从传统硬件制造商转型为 AI 全栈方案提供商。",
      "explanation": "通过提出“混合式人工智能”战略，整合个人 AI、企业 AI 和公共智能，联想旨在提供覆盖从硬件到软件、从个人到企业的完整 AI 解决方案。"
    },
    {
      "point": "推出个人超级智能体 Lenovo Qira，实现 AI 体验的系统级跨越。",
      "explanation": "Qira 集成了模型编排、智能体核心引擎和多智能体协作，能跨设备、跨应用理解用户意图并主动执行任务，是联想 AI 战略的核心产品。"
    },
    {
      "point": "持续创新并引领硬件形态，将硬件作为 AI 智能体验的载体。",
      "explanation": "联想展示了多种未来形态产品，如卷轴屏 PC、AI 眼镜、折叠屏手机，体现了其“软件驱动硬件”的理念，及对人机交互新形式的探索。"
